Description: Patched PostgreSQL 17 core for Babelfish
 Babelfish for PostgreSQL requires a patched PostgreSQL core to support
 T-SQL protocol/language hooks.
 .
 This package ships Babelfish patched PostgreSQL 17.8 under /usr/babelfish-17.

